TITLE: Episode 57 - Bloody Revolutions Never Last
DESCRIPTION: Maddie is out with THD... again, but not to worry. Jessie joined by THE Jessica Green of the Jessica Green show and Cam Harless of Make Liberty Great Again. Together they compare the French and Russian revolutions and the lessons we should have learned from that history. They also talk scary movies and possible philosophical themes. This episode goes deep.
